summary: adds a mini quest with a nice reward.
descriptionHtml:
The greybeards have intercepted a letter. It\'s in High Hrothgar on the table. You better read it.

the reward for this mini-quest is a powerfull staff with dragon powers (not OP in master/expert), a sword that damages stamina and magicka, wearable greybeard robes that reduce time between shouts, fortify health, stamina and magicka regen and add resistance to spells, they are light armor.  

please leave feedback if you have any problems or if you like the mod!
author: JMaarse
